{"tid":128360,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有睇nocturnal animals?","createTime":"2017-02-20T17:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T09:19:49.000Z","uid":2545,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f421aa5014230848e5fdbe342a197152bce285b5","tid":128360,"uid":2545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:42:19.000Z","msg":"睇完覺得TOM FORD都幾勁<br />\n由FASHION跳去做導演拍過2套戲, 2套都廣受好評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (另一套係a single man, colin firth做)<br />\n今次呢套係base on小說改編 我冇睇過本書所以評論唔到拍唔拍到小說既味道出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n純粹以睇戲既角度黎講, 首先呢套戲既選角真係好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAmy Adams第一次睇佢係睇enchanted, 之後佢拍既戲做D角色都幾多樣化, 今次呢套佢都做得幾好, 一貫水準, 特別係最尾果幕既神情<br />\nJake就十分之合適做呢套戲果個主角, 性格設定同佢比人既形象都好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 優柔寡斷 弱雞, 佢做內心掙扎戲都好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個人覺得佢每拍一套戲演技都有進步咁<br />\n最後aaron johnson真係值得拎best supporting actor, 做痴線佬做得好出色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇到我有幾幕都驚驚地佢, 真係癲癲地<br />\nMichael Shannon就一貫老戲骨啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除左選角, 成套戲既用色、格調同音樂都好特別, 個人感覺好迎合到套戲既主線 - 男主角寫果本小說既故事線, 好有效咁加重懸疑感<br />\nTom Ford做開fashion可能對於用色真係特別拿手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n套戲女主角既衣服顏色同埋個妝都好表達到佢內心既折騰<br />\n<br />\n推介大家可以睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個人就鍾意Amy Adams呢套戲既演出多D, 好過arrival<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa2a23ffe5a0ff298a19f7273368f1e9a6bafa43","tid":128360,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:44:11.000Z","msg":"好正，復仇<br />\n<br />\n女主就係一個臭西"},{"pid":"e2bbd2f39b3aceaff3f9be56249a3ccb1541aeef","tid":128360,"uid":2545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:26:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好正，復仇<br />\n<br />\n女主就係一個臭西</blockquote><br />\nYES主題就係報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"466c7079ba2ca32235b09db19e8970a382893e39","tid":128360,"uid":57007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:45:54.000Z","msg":"戲院唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\nItunes 同google 出咗 <br />\n好失望"},{"pid":"b742180f3cf284ff8c8b1cc5d3dddcede0e1f349","tid":128360,"uid":80109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:10:20.000Z","msg":"都唔明咁既卡士點解會唔上正場<br />\n睇完個餘韻仲係度 演員做得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4e7a7fdc230499a4d80380c38a4535e99396048","tid":128360,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:19:49.000Z","msg":"復仇主線無乜驚喜，反而諷剌藝術界既虛偽脆弱果度幾過癮<br />\nCarlos: Susan, enjoy the absurdity of our world. It's a lot less painful. Believe me, our world is a lot less painful than the real world.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nMichael Shannon呢個神經刀真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}